Title: Lost in the Sea
Descriptions: Hi my name is "Jasmine". It all happened so fast. One minute I was stirring my stew, the next… well, the next the bandits took over, it came out of nowhere. I remember the screams, the crashing metal, the smell… then nothing but the endless red of blood...

I'm still shaky %1, but I'm safe now. i just want to go to your camp… it's a strange place, but it will be home for now. I owe a debt of gratitude to the one who found me. They risked their own safety to pull me from the wreckage, to bring me back to the others. I'm still trying to understand everything that happened, but I know this: I'm not alone anymore.
